Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:39.12,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:47.59,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:55.76,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:03.94,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:10.85,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:21.29,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:30.87,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
